  "description": "<p><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>🚨</strong></a><strong> URGENT HIRING - PETROL STATION 🚨</strong></p><p><strong>Position: Sales Assistant 销售助理</strong></p><p><strong>Salary Range: $2305 - $2500</strong></p><p><u><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>●       Customer service delivery 提供客服服务</p><p>●       Operate the Point of Sales system accurately 要操作POS销售系统</p><p>●       Stock Replenishing & expiry date check 库存补充，陈列和检查商品有效期</p><p>●       Doing receiving and checking of convenience store goods 货物签收与点算</p><p>●       General housekeeping and cleaning at station 油站的基本清理</p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>●       Full Time & Part Time position !!!! 全职和兼职!!!</p><p>●       Physical fit 身体状况良好</p><p>●       Start work immediately 能够即刻开工</p><p>●       Work Schedule: Shift work, weekends and public holidays 轮班制, 可在周末或公共假期上班</p><p>●       No experience required 无经验者欢迎申请</p><p>●       Welcome residents to apply 欢迎居民申请</p><p>●       Location 工作地点: Multiple Location (多个地点)</p><p><u><strong>Benefits 福利</strong></u></p><p>●       Medical Coverage 医疗保险</p><p>●       Teamwork allowance 团队津贴</p><p>●       Festive Allowance 节日津贴</p><p>●       Other attractive Incentive 其他津贴</p><p>●       Uniform provided 提供工作制服</p><p>*** If you are interested, please call <em><strong>Mr.Shariff (91871435)， Ms. Mala (87113400), Mr.Hamley (85757832)</strong></em> </p><p>***有意者请联系 <em><strong>Mr. Shariff (91871435)， Ms. Mala(87113400), Mr. Hamley (85757832)</strong></em> </p>",
